name: ISAYAMA LABS GENESIS FOUNDERS' COIN
description: The ISAYAMA LABS GENESIS FOUNDERS' COIN is a utility token that, once burned, gives its owner the ability to receive one edition from every OBJKT that ISAYAMA LABS mints airdropped to their wallet address for the next 10 OBJKTs ISAYAMA LABS mints (each edition worth at least 0.5 tez). For example, if user_1 bought a GENESIS FOUNDERS' COIN on 11/20/25 at 3AM and burnt it on 12/25/25 at 11:59PM, user_1 would recieve a single edition from every OBJKT that ISAYAMA LABS mints airdropped to their wallet address for the next 10 OBJKTs ISAYAMA LABS mints after 12/25/25 after 11:59PM
